---
---
<section class="py-24 bg-[#0a0b0d]">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-16 text-white tracking-tight">
      Dale un vistazo a nuestro <span class="text-primary">blog</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 auto-rows-[280px]">
      <!-- Main Featured Post (Left) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-4 md:row-span-2 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-white/5">
        <img
          src="/blog-1.png"
          alt="Eventos Masivos"
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/90 via-black/40 to-transparent"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8 w-full">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Eventos Masivos</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/70 line-clamp-3 mb-6">
            En los grandes festivales musicales como los que reúnen a decenas de miles de personas durante varios días la tecnología es el motor silencioso que permite que todo funcione...
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white border border-white/20 hover:border-primary transition-colors py-2 px-6 rounded-full group/btn">
            Leer Articulo 
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover/btn:translate-x-1 group-hover/btn:-translate-y-1"><path d="M7 7h10v10"/><path d="M7 17 17 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Secondary Post (Top Right) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-8 md:row-span-1 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/5 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden group">
        <div class="h-full overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/blog-2.png" alt="Conexión Híbrida" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" />
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 flex flex-col justify-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Conexión Híbrida</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/50 mb-6">
            La conectividad híbrida surge justo para resolver ese punto débil. La idea es sencilla: no depender de un único enlace...
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold text-white border border-white/10 hover:border-primary transition-colors py-1.5 px-4 rounded-full self-start">
            Leer Articulo <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 7h10v10"/><path d="M7 17 17 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text Highlight (Bottom Middle) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-5 md:row-span-1 bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/5 rounded-3xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-between group hover:border-primary/20 transition-all">
        <div>
          <div class="w-10 h-1 bg-white/20 mb-6 transition-all group-hover:w-20 group-hover:bg-primary"></div>
          <p class="text-base text-white/80 leading-relaxed italic">
            "Durante los últimos años, he observado cambios significativos en la colaboración dentro del entorno laboral, los cuales han traído consigo interesantes desafíos y oportunidades..."
          </p>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold text-white border border-white/10 hover:border-primary transition-colors py-1.5 px-4 rounded-full self-start">
          Leer Articulo <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 7h10v10"/><path d="M7 17 17 7"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Image Only/Small Card (Bottom Right) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-3 md:row-span-1 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-white/5 relative group">
        <!-- We use the same image or a third one if preferred. Let's use a stylized version or just the second one for now -->
        <img src="/blog-2.png" alt="Empresa" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110 blur-[1px] group-hover:blur-0" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40 flex items-center justify-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
           <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase">Ver más</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
